google+ description:
The standard by which other are judged...since 1939!Founded
in 1939 by Charles “Buck” Ruff , Ruff Roofers started as a residential
contractor, but by the 1950’s Ruff Roofers was strongly engaged in commercial
work as well, by the late 1950’s, Buck’s son Charles W. Ruff took the company
reigns and advanced the company’s growth until 1996, when his son Timothy Ruff
became the owner and President. The torch was passed to his sons, Tim and Rob, who
embody the same commitment to integrity, craftsmanship and customer satisfaction
as their ancestors. Ruff is proud to be in its fourth generation of leadership
and over seven decades of success.Today Ruff Roofers is an industry leader and provides
a wide range of roofing and contractor services.  Our services are no longer limited by
traditional roofing, but also include: roof restorations, custom metal fabrication,
hot rubberized asphalt waterproofing, vertical wall systems, masonry
restorations and other building envelope related needs.  We are known throughout the industry by both
our clients and peers as an organization with the capability and track record
to perform the most challenging projects.

google+ description: Thomas Roofing Company is a Maryland based family business steeped in tradition since 1924. Our commitment to excellence in providing complete roofing services in Maryland is based on quality workmanship, seamless execution and the highest level of customer satisfaction. Family values of truth and honesty are the cornerstone of our business practice with both our customers and employees. Thomas Roofing maintains its tradition of high standards of excellence through in-house and product manufacturer training that keeps workmen up to date with the developments in the home improvement industry. . Thomas Roofing is proud to be among only 2 percent of roofing contractors who have earned GAF Master Elite™ Certification.
